sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Web as Web App
    participant IDP as Identity Provider
    participant API as API
    participant DB as Database

    User->>Web: Open app
    Web->>IDP: Redirect to login
    User->>IDP: Submit credentials
    IDP-->>Web: Auth code / token response
    Web->>API: Request with bearer token
    API->>IDP: Validate token and claims
    IDP-->>API: Token valid + roles
    API->>DB: Read or write resource/comment
    DB-->>API: Result
    API-->>Web: Response
    Web-->>User: Render updated view
